		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />greetings from Brazil.<br />I came to share a repro cart that I researched a long time to be able to do it.<br />This is a megaman x2 + x3 copy using a x2 donor.<br />I will not share the ROM, but all information needed to do it is found in this forum.<br />memory used was a 29l3211<br /><br /><a href="https://ibb.co/jJO2r8" class="postlink"><img src="https://preview.ibb.co/gym0do/Whats_App_Image_2018_07_25_at_01_17_20.jpg" alt="Image" /></a><br /><br />I apologize for the bad photo. but the two games work perfectly and no error is presented in the CX4 Test<br /><br />attached is the image of the adapter<br /><a href="https://ibb.co/b9JhPT" class="postlink"><img src="https://preview.ibb.co/gYN94T/down_Img_1.png" alt="Image" /></a>

		

