		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My main concern is about the console itself, since it's internal parts are not very easy to replace.<br />I think the level shifters can be incorporated on the same board that does the pin convertion.<br /><br />Not trying to get too off-topic, but are special chips like SA1 and SDD1 3,3v tolerant on the ROM part?<br />I'm probably wrong, but it seems that the ROM is totally accessed through the chip, is it?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
